在音樂中，'''含七小三度'''（{{lang-en|'''septimal minor third'''}}）{{audio|Septimal minor third on C.mid|播放}}，亦稱''下小三度''（這是[[赫爾曼·馮·亥姆霍茲|赫爾曼·馮·亥姆霍茲]]的叫法<ref>Hermann L. F Von Helmholtz (2007). On the Sensations of Tone, p.195. ISBN 1-60206-639-6.</ref><ref>Royal Society (Great Britain) (1880, digitized Feb 26, 2008). ''Proceedings of the Royal Society of London, Volume 30'', p.531. Harvard University.</ref>），是比例為7:6的[[音程|音程]]<ref>Partch, Harry (1979). ''[[Genesis_of_a_Music|Genesis of a Music]]'', p.68. ISBN 0-306-80106-X.</ref>。這音程折合267[[音分|音分]]，比純律的[[小三度|小三度]]（6:5）小一個{{link-en|含七四分一音|Septimal quarter tone|36:35的四分一音}}。[[二十四平均律|二十四平均律]]中的五個四分一音（{{Audio|Five quarter tones on C.mid|播放}}）折合250音分，和這音程相近。

含七小三度是[[泛音列|泛音列]]中從第六個泛音到第七個的音程。[[十二平均律|十二平均律]]的音中，除了基音和第二泛音外，與其他音都不和諧<ref>Leta E. Miller, Fredric Lieberman (2006). ''Lou Harrison'', p.72. ISBN 0-252-03120-2. "Among the most striking intervals are...the narrow 7:6 subminor third...The seventh harmonic...was problematic in all Western tuning systems. The interval it forms with the sixth harmonic [7:6 subminor third] is smaller than a minor third but larger than a major second. To cite a specific example: the seventh harmonic of C lies partway between A and B-flat. Sounding with the sixth harmonic (G), it forms a 7:6 subminor third of 267 cents--33 cents smaller than the equal-tempered minor third, itself 16 cents smaller than the pure 6:5 minor third. This 7:6 interval is thus nearly a quarter tone smaller than the pure minor third (33 + 16 = 49 cents)."</ref>。這音程比6:5的三度更黑暗但亦討人喜歡。用這個三度而成的[[三和弦|三和弦]]稱為含七小三和弦或下小三和弦{{audio|Septimal minor triad on C.mid|播放}}。

在[[中庸全音律|中庸全音律]]中，含七小三度以[[增二度|增二度]]的形式出現。Tunings of the meantone fifth in the neighborhood of [[quarter-comma_meantone|quarter-comma meantone]] will give three septimal minor thirds among the twelve minor thirds of the tuning; since the [[wolf_fifth|wolf fifth]] appears with an ordinary minor third, this entails there are three septimal minor triads, eight ordinary minor triads and one triad containing the [[wolf_fifth|wolf fifth]] arising from an ordinary minor third followed by a [[septimal_major_third|septimal major third]].

==在平均律及非西方音階中的含七小三度==

在西方音樂最普遍的[[十二平均律|十二平均律]]中沒有這個音程，[[二十四平均律|二十四平均律]]亦沒有這個音程。然而，[[十九平均律|十九平均律]]、[[二十二平均律|二十二平均律]]、[[三十一平均律|三十一平均律]]、[[四十一平均律|四十一平均律]]、[[五十三平均律|五十三平均律]]和[[七十二平均律|七十二平均律]]一個比一個有更接近含七小三度的音程。

有好幾個非西方[[純律|純律]]音階有準確的含七小三度，例如{{link-en|哈利·帕爾奇||Harry Partch}}所創立的四十三音階。

